---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="System Stories Â· Real Problems, Systematic Solutions"
  description="Case studies of founder-built internal systems: dashboards, backend platforms, and operational tools that solve real business problems."
>
  <section style="padding: 80px 24px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center;">System Stories</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #b0b0c0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 64px; text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      Real problems, systematic solutions, documented outcomes.
    </p>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: 32px;">
      <!-- System Story 1 -->
      <div style="background: #1a1a23; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%;">
        <div style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; color: #3a8bba; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">Dashboard System</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #f0f0f5;">Replacing Manual Reporting</h2>
        <p style="color: #b0b0c0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-grow: 1;">
          A SaaS founder was spending 4 hours daily merging data from 5 different spreadsheets to understand business performance.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Dashboard</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Automation</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Reporting</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #2a2a35; padding-top: 24px;">
          <div style="color: #808090; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
          <div style="color: #f0f0f5; font-weight: 500;">Daily reporting time reduced from 4 hours to 10 minutes</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- System Story 2 -->
      <div style="background: #1a1a23; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%;">
        <div style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; color: #3a8bba; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">Backend Platform</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #f0f0f5;">Operations Automation System</h2>
        <p style="color: #b0b0c0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-grow: 1;">
          An e-commerce operator was manually processing orders across 3 platforms, leading to errors and customer service issues.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">API Integration</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Workflow Automation</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Error Handling</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #2a2a35; padding-top: 24px;">
          <div style="color: #808090; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
          <div style="color: #f0f0f5; font-weight: 500;">Order processing automated, errors reduced by 92%</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- System Story 3 -->
      <div style="background: #1a1a23; border: 1px solid #2a2a35; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%;">
        <div style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; color: #3a8bba; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">Internal Tool</div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #f0f0f5;">Client Onboarding Portal</h2>
        <p style="color: #b0b0c0; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; flex-grow: 1;">
          A service business was using 8 different tools for client onboarding, causing confusion and delays.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Portal</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Document Management</div>
          <div style="display: inline-block; background: rgba(58, 139, 186, 0.1); color: #3a8bba; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Notifications</div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #2a2a35; padding-top: 24px;">
          <div style="color: #808090; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">Outcome</div>
          <div style="color: #f0f0f5; font-weight: 500;">Onboarding time reduced from 2 weeks to 3 days</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 64px;">
      <p style="color: #808090; font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        These are anonymized examples. Real stories include more detail about challenges and solutions.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" style="background: #3a8bba; color: white; padding: 16px 32px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: inline-block;">Describe Your Challenge</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
